[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_vp3gf")
release_version = "v1.2.7"
notes = "[TITLE]Engine
Updated to Godot version 4.6.2
[TITLE]Bosses
Fully clearing the Skull Finder round of the Head of Security boss fight will end the encounter without needing to face the following two rounds
[TITLE]Tweaks
The Organic Gags anomaly now applies a 10% boost to each gag track's effectiveness rather than just your Damage stat
Added a backups system for save files, saving the three most recent versions of your settings and overall game progress
  You can find them in the backups folder in the save directory
The Clowns in the Faulty Factory feel approximately 10% funnier
Made some visual improvements to the Doodle
[TITLE]Bugfixes
Fixed an issue where the \"I'm Stuck!\" button would appear during encounters with The Liquidator
Fixed the inconsistent timing on the Evil Eye battle movie
Fixed an issue where Clerk Clara's Trap boost would not apply to Trap gags upgraded by Mini Blinds
Fixed a few issues where gag points could exceed the carry limit in battle
Fixed an issue where HP Change text could appear in battle when no HP Change occurred, showing a \"0\"
Custom Cogs' unique suit textures will no longer override the suit of the base Cog in The Faulty Factory
Toon speech bubbles no longer animate with the Toon's body
Connector rooms in facilities are now properly seeded
[TITLE]For Modders
The Null Cog department should now be functional
[TITLE]Hotfix #1
Fixed Yesman's suit textures not loading
[TITLE]Hotfix #2
Fixed Head of Security handing out free wins to anyone just for beating Skull Finder normally
[TITLE]Hotfix #3
Fixed Head of Security's win music not playing upon standard victories"
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://d1j0hh6tsgy0r"
